     <div type="reminder_of_crucifixion">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <p>
      <figure>
</figure>
   </p>
   <l>The heretikes indeuoure is, by al the meanes they may,</l>
   <l>The memorie of Christ his death, to we and put away:</l>
   <l>And therefore his Crosse, and howe he dyd dye</l>
   <l>To take out of sight, all shameles, they trye.</l>
   <l>But thowe that arte Christian, of Christ his death see</l>
   <l>The passion here printed, as picture to thee.</l>
</div>
